reviewText:
If I had to rate the enhaced version of this game without ever playing the original I would easly give this a 5 out of 5. That being said though having played the original Baldur's Gate 2 and Throne of Bhaal many time over, I would give the enhanced version a 3 out of 5.

I give the enhanced" version a lower rating for a few facts;

1. I have noticed far more bugs in the enhanced version of the game then I ever did in the origional
